OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMuch of England and Wales will
OL,6,Fbe dry with plenty on sunshine. A
OL,7,Fwidely hot or even very hot day with
OL,8,Fplaces reaching the low 30s in the
OL,9,Fsoutheast. Cloudier in the northwest
OL,10,Fof Scotland with rain at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine and dry night for most
OL,13,Fwith clear skies across England and
OL,14,FWales. Cloudier in the northwest with
OL,15,Fpatchy outbreaks of rain in Scotland.
OL,16,FAnother very mild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
