OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy in northwest Scotland
OL,6,Fwith rain at times, otherwise most
OL,7,Fplaces seeing lots of sunshine. It
OL,8,Fremains hot, especially in the south
OL,9,Fbut cooler along the coasts.
